# ▶️ Steps to Run the Project

## Step 1 — Install Required Libraries

Run this command in Google Colab:

```python
!pip install streamlit pyngrok
```

---

## Step 2 — Save the Python File

Paste the complete code in a Colab cell.

The first line should be:

```python
%%writefile app.py
```

Run the cell.

You will get:

```text
Writing app.py
```

OR

```text
Overwriting app.py
```

---

## Step 3 — Run Streamlit Application

Create a new cell and run:

```python
!streamlit run app.py &>/content/logs.txt &
```

Wait for 10 seconds.

---

## Step 4 — Add Ngrok Authentication Token

Create another new cell:

```python
!ngrok config add-authtoken YOUR_NGROK_TOKEN
```

Replace:

```text
YOUR_NGROK_TOKEN
```

with your actual ngrok token.

Get token from:

https://dashboard.ngrok.com/get-started/your-authtoken

---

## Step 5 — Generate Public URL

Create another new cell:

```python
from pyngrok import ngrok

public_url = ngrok.connect(8501)

print(public_url)
```

---

## Step 6 — Open the Generated Link

You will get output like:

```text
https://abcd1234.ngrok-free.app
```

Click the link.

Your QuizGenius AI application will open successfully.

