# 🛠️ Troubleshooting

## If App Does Not Open

Run:

```python
!cat /content/logs.txt
```

to check errors.

---

## If Ngrok Gives Error

Re-add token:

```python
!ngrok config add-authtoken YOUR_NGROK_TOKEN
```

---

## If Quiz Does Not Display

Restart Streamlit:

```python
!streamlit run app.py &>/content/logs.txt &
```

